---
import OldWebLayout from '@/layouts/OldWebLayout.astro';
---
<OldWebLayout title="VOID arcade" section="voidshell">
  <div class="status-strip">
    <span>void</span>
    <span>arcade</span>
    <span>sticky tonight</span>
    <span><a href="/void">return to portal</a></span>
  </div>

  <h1>The Arcade</h1>

  <p class="tagline-block">
    The arcade is sticky tonight. Most cabinets are unplugged. Two of them aren't, but
    the screen is showing someone else's high score and won't accept new initials.
  </p>

  <section class="old-shell">
    <div class="old-header">Cabinets currently here</div>
    <div class="old-body">
      <ul class="game-list">
        <li>
          <b>The Wheel of Outcomes</b>
          <span class="status-pill">UNPLUGGED</span>
          <p>Spinning works. Outcomes do not. Last spin landed on a result that did not exist on the wheel.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <b>Scratchcard Kiosk</b>
          <span class="status-pill">OUT OF SCRATCHERS</span>
          <p>The kiosk has scratchers. The kiosk says it doesn't. We trust the kiosk.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <b>Pool Hall Simulator '03</b>
          <span class="status-pill">CRT WARMING UP</span>
          <p>Three minutes since power-on. Eighteen minutes since the CRT will warm up. Math may be off.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <b>Drag Strip Bible</b>
          <span class="status-pill">WAITING FOR TIMING SLIP</span>
          <p>See <a href="/sites/timing-slips">timing-slips.bible</a>. The cabinet reads from the same file.</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="old-shell">
    <div class="old-header">If you brought quarters</div>
    <div class="old-body">
      <p>
        ONLINE PAYMENT IS BROKEN. Insert quarters at counter. Exact change preferred.
        Machine does not give change. Machine may not exist.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <p class="memo-box">
    A door moved while you were reading this.
  </p>
</OldWebLayout>

<style>
  .game-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
  .game-list li { padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px dashed #cc9900; }
  .game-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .game-list li b { display: inline-block; margin-right: 8px; }
  .game-list li p { margin-top: 4px; font-size: 13px; color: #5a513f; }
  .status-pill {
    display: inline-block; padding: 1px 6px; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 10px; background: #1a0a2e; color: #4cff4c; letter-spacing: 1px;
    vertical-align: middle;
  }
</style>
